  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000056",
    "sentence": "十月，兵畢至隴西。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000057",
    "sentence": "十一月，並進。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000058",
    "sentence": "羌虜大破，斬首數千級，餘皆走出塞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000059",
    "sentence": "兵未決間，漢復發募士萬人，拜定襄太守韓安國為建威將軍。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      },
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000060",
    "sentence": "未進，聞羌破，還。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000061",
    "sentence": "上曰：「羌虜破散創艾，亡逃出塞，其罷吏士，頗留屯田，備要害處。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_079_000062",
    "sentence": "明年二月，奉世還京師，更為左將軍光祿勳如故。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 14,
        "end": 16
      }
    ]
